title: [1508521049] An Expert's Guide to Mushrooms - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon enlists the help of mushroom expert Fred Foster to explain the subtleties in the many forms of mushrooms that are available for cooking.

Subscribe for weekly cooking videos.
